<br>
Level 61 wiz would probably use Lure of Thunder, since it's the only PoP lure at 61. With the 66% nerf in place, LoT does 717 damage. Since the level 61 player is attacking a level 65, he'd get a 30% damage bonus for attacking a higher level player, which brings his damage to 932.<br>
The level 65, using Lure of Ro would be doing 717.<br>
<br>
I'd take the level 65 1 cast to make up for the level 61's damage bonus. It's not as big of an advantage as you think it is.<br>
Also, how likely is it that a level 61 will have Focus IV items? From my experience, it's not too likely. A level 65 still has a large advantage over the 61.<br>
<br>
Another thing you're totally forgetting about is the fact that players won't stay at specific levels just so they have that bonus over a level 65. They will still level up, so in the end, that level 61 will eventually be 65, and the playing field is once again level.<br>
